        <abstract>
            <p>CD has a low opinion of British entomologists.</p>
            <p>Lyell’s ingenious difficulties with natural selection show he is in earnest.</p>
            <p>Asks JDH to observe beetles and variation of stripes in mules on his Syrian tour.</p>
